  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will start the rehabilitation process for hundreds of devastated homeowners whose homes were destroyed in the Carlton Complex Fire that swept through Washington State in July 2014 - the largest in its history. IsraAID and its US partner Team Rubicon will engage in debris removal and the retrieval of personal belongings. This action, and its timing, are crucial to breaking the cycle of overwhelming devastating suffered by the homeowner, and minimizing the chances of long-term trauma.</narrative>
  </description>
